title: "Is Co-Fermentation Cheating? Wrong Question. Most Coffee Still Can't Explain Its Processing"
date: "2026-04-15"
description: "The specialty coffee industry is fighting over co-ferments before it has built a real processing taxonomy for ordinary coffee."
